metadata.name: Money Museum Banknote
metadata.description:
Money Museum NFT is a platform that offers Vintage Banknote NFTs, each of which is linked to an individual actual Vintage Banknote that is stored by Money Museum.
 Through the Money Museum platform, Money Museum NFT owners can exchange their NFTs for that physical vintage banknote, subject to Money Museumâ€™s Terms of Service & Conditions which includes certain important restrictions.
